Package ui.components

Class CartEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.components.CartEntry
  • public class CartEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an entry in a shopping cart. Each CartEntry holds a MenuItem and a JSpinner for its quantity selection.
